'''玛莎拉蒂吉博力'''（Maserati Ghibli）是[[玛莎拉蒂|玛莎拉蒂]]2013年开始生产的一款[[行政车|行政车]]<ref name="TELEGRAPH">{{cite journal |last=English |first=Andrew |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/motoring/car-manufacturers/maserati/10146075/Maserati-Ghibli-review.html |title=Maserati Ghibli review |journal=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=27 June 2013 |author= |access-date=2020-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715135310/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/motoring/car-manufacturers/maserati/10146075/Maserati-Ghibli-review.html |archive-date=2020-07-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2013年[[上海车展|上海车展]]上首次面世<ref name="autoblog Shanghai">{{cite web |url=http://www.autoblog.com/2013/04/20/2014-maserati-ghibli-shanghai-2013/ |website=autoblog.com |title=2014 Maserati Ghibli snarls in Shanghai |date=20 April 2013 |accessdate=16 November 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718123647/https://www.autoblog.com/2013/04/20/2014-maserati-ghibli-shanghai-2013/ |archive-date=2020-07-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这是玛莎拉蒂1994年[[玛莎拉蒂Biturbo|玛莎拉蒂Biturbo]]停产后重新生产的一款中型豪华汽车<ref name="C&D1">{{cite web |url=http://www.caranddriver.com/news/2014-maserati-ghibli-photos-and-info-news |website=Car & Driver |title=2014 Maserati Ghibli: It really is a baby Quattroporte. |date=April 2013 |accessdate=16 November 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180809205521/https://www.caranddriver.com/news/2014-maserati-ghibli-photos-and-info-news |archive-date=2018-08-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它和第六代[[玛莎拉蒂总裁|玛莎拉蒂总裁]]的结构一样，但轴距短{{convert|200|mm|in|1|abbr=on}}，车身短{{convert|290|mm|in|1|abbr=on}}<ref name="autoblog Shanghai" />。

